skills.description:
Attacks all enemies 3 times, each time dealing Physical DMG equal to <color=#82C65D>120/150/180/210/240%</color> of self's ATK and inflicts the enemy targets with 10 seconds of Timid.
Timid: Decreases the target's Physical and Magic DEF equal to <color=#82C65D>15% </color>of self's ATK for 10s.

skills.name: Noble Glory
skills.description: When dealing damage, inflicts extra Physical DMG equal to <color=#82C65D>15/30%</color> of self's ATK.

equipment.name: Odomera
equipment.description: A sword handed down over generations in the Kingdom of Lochaber. Reserved for the heir to the throne.
equipment.effect: After combat starts, ATK increases by <color=#82C65D>1.65/1.8/1.95/2.1/2.25/2.4%</color> every 5s, stacks up to 15 times.
equipment.evolution: (Evolving the current Character's Level will also increase an Attribute by <color=#82C65D>0/0.15/0.3/0.45</color>%)

backstories: A noble with a graceful bearing, she stands out from any crowd.

She travels around the Kingdom of Lochaber to learn about the plight of the people in preparation for her ascension to the throne. When the monsters invade, she returns to the capital to lead a fight against them.
Knowing that it would be hard for Lochaber to fight the growing number of monsters alone, she leads a mission to various kingdoms in a bid to form an alliance against the monsters.

Watching people celebrate the new year in a foreign land fills her with nostalgia. Then she reminds herself that emotions and weakness won't do any good for her kingdom, and that her mission is still unfinished.

bonds.reward: Magic DEF Enhancement: Increases Magic DEF by <color=#82C65D>72</color>
Physical DEF Enhancement: Increases Physical DEF by <color=#82C65D>72</color>

voicelines.name: Interaction 1
voicelines.description: My carefully groomed hair is all messed up...

voicelines.name: Interaction 2
voicelines.description: You... You... What are you doing!?

voicelines.name: Interaction 3
voicelines.description: Knock it off! Stop pinching my face.

voicelines.name: Interaction 4
voicelines.description: Disrespecting royalty is a serious crime!

voicelines.name: Interaction 5
voicelines.description: Please keep your distance. You're making me uncomfortable...

voicelines.name: Level UP
voicelines.description: I've gotten stronger. Father would be proud if he saw me now.

voicelines.name: Ascend
voicelines.description: I've come a long way from my noble origins.

voicelines.name: Evolve
voicelines.description: You haven't seen half of what I can do.

voicelines.name: Give Gifts 1
voicelines.description: Thanks for the gift. I'll take it.

voicelines.name: Give Gifts 2
voicelines.description: We share the same taste. Incredible!

voicelines.name: Idle
voicelines.description: The enemy is coming. This is no time to let down your guard.

voicelines.name: Witch Courtyard 1
voicelines.description: Such unique decor. I see you've got taste.

voicelines.name: Witch Courtyard 2
voicelines.description: This is where the party will be held after the battle, right?

voicelines.name: Witch Courtyard 3
voicelines.description: Relax, this is barely a warm-up.

voicelines.name: Witch Courtyard 4
voicelines.description: See? Easy-peasy.

voicelines.name: Debut
voicelines.description: I'm Carol, heir to the Kingdom of Lochaber. It is my duty to protect the people of this land.

voicelines.name: Formation
voicelines.description: Want to fight together?

voicelines.name: Explore Main Story
voicelines.description: Monsters still plague this land. I shall destroy them with my sword.

voicelines.name: Altar
voicelines.description: Resting is not slacking—it's getting ready for the next battle.

voicelines.name: Talk 1
voicelines.description: I hear the plea of the people, and I'm willing to do everything for them.

voicelines.name: Talk 2
voicelines.description: If my singing could heal people's scarred souls, I wouldn't have to swing my sword and partake in bloodshed every day...

voicelines.name: Talk 3
voicelines.description: This world can only be saved by the light in people's hearts. All I can do is lead people to that light.

voicelines.name: Talk 4
voicelines.description: Two things I can't stand: monsters ravaging the world and evil corrupting the human mind.

voicelines.name: Emotion 1
voicelines.description: (Smile)

voicelines.name: Emotion 2
voicelines.description: How rude!

voicelines.name: Self-intro
voicelines.description: Whatever we're up against, we must stay hopeful—it's the only way to receive grace from the goddess. May she answer my prayers and bless Lochaber.

voicelines.name: Battle Begins
voicelines.description: I fight for the future of the kingdom!

voicelines.name: Skill 1
voicelines.description: Bloom!

voicelines.name: Skill 2
voicelines.description: My sword guides my way!

voicelines.name: Assaulted
voicelines.description: Ah...

voicelines.name: Revive
voicelines.description: This can't be the end...

voicelines.name: Victory
voicelines.description: I will not fail. For justice always prevails.

voicelines.name: Defeat
voicelines.description: For the future of the kingdom, I must survive...

voicelines.name: Target Eliminated
voicelines.description: Begone!

voicelines.name: Bond 1
voicelines.description: Huh? You want to fight alongside me? But I don't know you...

voicelines.name: Bond 2
voicelines.description: My people are suffering from the monsters plaguing this land. It is up to the royal family to protect them.

voicelines.name: Bond 3
voicelines.description: It's an honor to fight alongside me, you say? You flatter me. Eliminating the monsters is not a one-man job, but a team effort.

voicelines.name: Bond 4
voicelines.description: You're interesting. I'd love to invite you to my party in the capital and introduce you to everyone.

voicelines.name: Bond 5
voicelines.description: It's praying time. Come pray with me. Dear goddess, who guards this land: I pray that you give us light and hope and grant us the strength to save the people from their suffering and build a better future for all of us.

name: Snowshine
title: Sweet Delivery

skills.name: Magic of Love
skills.description: Increases the DMG taken of all enemies by <color=#82C65D>22/24/26/28/30%</color> for 10s, and restores 1 Chaos Energy.

skills.name: Blessings of Love
skills.description: Restores 1 Order Energy, and heals all allies for <color=#82C65D>360/400/440/480/520%</color> of self's ATK.

skills.name: Sweet and Sour Surprise
skills.description: When using skills, there is a <color=#82C65D>10/20%</color> chance to restore 1 Chaos Energy.

equipment.name: Sweet Heartbeat
equipment.description: Snowshine's newly developed dessert. Popular among young people.
equipment.effect: Increases DMG Dealt of all allies by <color=#82C65D>1/2/3/4/5/6%</color>.
equipment.evolution: (Evolving the current Character's Level will also increase DMG by <color=#82C65D>0/1/2/3</color>%)

backstories: Snowshine is the child of a human and an elf. Because of the human blood in her body, she was ostracized in the Forest of Elves.

Snowshine likes to use her power to make delicious desserts since she was a child. When she grew up, she opened a dessert store in a human town, which was widely loved by local residents, and even some gourmets went long distances to have a taste.

The elves considered Snowbirds, who were integrated into human society, to be an alien. However, because the elves themselves live far from human society, Snowshine did not suffer from their harassment.
Recently, she has developed new desserts to prepare for the upcoming hot sale in anticipation of the human holiday.

backstories: Born in the famous gastronomic city Esmeralda in the Kingdom of Belgica, she has a unique gift for tasting sweets, which she probably owes to her special bloodline.
It's said that any shop that earns Geisha's approval will thrive, which some people guess is a blessing from elves.
As the festival approaches, the owners of sweets shops in all the cities of the Kingdom of Belgica are asking about the whereabouts of Geisha, hoping to receive her review and approval.
Recently, Geisha was told that someone was planning to cause trouble at the festival ceremony. Apparently she is not going to let anyone get in the way of people enjoying food.
